Popular skit maker Cute Abiola has taken to his Instagram story to motivate his over 4 million followers. Lawyer Kunle, as he is fondly called, recently shared some motivation tips with his fans.   INEC withholds officers’ allowances     Anambra court orders Obiano, police to remove roadblocks     Sammie Okposo pulls down apology post   He wrote: “See ehn! I know my motivational quotes are too much these days. But let me drop another one. I know what I am seeing. And I know what I am saying too. “Whatever happens in your life, no matter how troubling things might seem, do not enter despair. I mean never have the feeling of no hope left for you. Even when all doors remain closed, God will open up a new path only for you. Be thankful! Pls pls. Na person wey give up, fuck up!”